  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grafton\" title=\"House Grafton\"><img alt=\"House Grafton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/50px-House_Grafton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/75px-House_Grafton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/100px-House_Grafton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Marq Grafton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grafton\" title=\"House Grafton\"><img alt=\"House Grafton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/50px-House_Grafton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/75px-House_Grafton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/100px-House_Grafton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Grafton\" title=\"House Grafton\">House Grafton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_Gulltown\" title=\"Taking of Gulltown\">Gulltown</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Marq Grafton</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Grafton\" title=\"House Grafton\">House Grafton</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marq_Grafton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>At the start of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>, Lord Grafton stayed loyal to King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> instead of following his liege, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>, into rebellion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_robert.E2.80.99s_rebellion.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_robert.E2.80.99s_rebellion.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Marq was slain by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> at the Gulltown walls when the rebels <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_Gulltown\" title=\"Taking of Gulltown\">took the city</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marq_Grafton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 9\">Chapter 9</a>, Davos I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_robert.E2.80.99s_rebellion.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_fall_of_the_dragons:_robert.E2.80.99s_rebellion.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &am